a kind of array jiska size define krne ki zarurat nahi aur size inc kr skte

CREATING ARRAYLIST
ArrayList < datatype > arr.name = new ArrayList<>();

SIZE OF AN ARRAY
arr.name.size();

GET VALUE OF AN INDEX
arr.name.get( index no )

CHANGE VALUE OF AN INDEX
arr.name.set( index, value )

ADD VALUE
arr.name.add( value )

ADD VALUE TO AN INDEX
arr.name.add( index no, value )
